ing: 1 (14 ounce) can artichoke hearts, drained and coarsely chopped
1 cup Dannon Oikos Plain Greek Nonfat Yogurt
1 cup coarsely chopped baby arugula leaves
Fresh cracked black pepper to taste
Grilled pita bread, cut into triangles, or pita chips
des: "A cool, creamy, no-bake dip loaded with artichokes and sun-dried tomatoes."
ins: Mix together artichokes, yogurt, Parmesan cheese, arugula, sun-dried tomatoes, garlic, and pepper. Refrigerate for at least one hour before serving for flavors to blend. Serve with grilled pita triangles or pita chips.
